# Fix for stable-sept-29 branch: Add explicit API endpoint to prevent localhost routing

This patch adds the `api: '/api/chat'` prop to useChat hook to ensure it uses relative paths
instead of potentially falling back to localhost.

Apply this to stable-sept-29 branch:

```typescript
// In components/chat.tsx, around line 48-50
const chatHook = useChat({
  id: CHAT_ID, // or id, depending on branch
  api: '/api/chat', // ADD THIS LINE - ensures relative path
  body: {
    id
  },
  // ... rest of config
})
```

